      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>Butcher is a longsword of immense power, given to Agamemnon by the goddess of magic herself. Only a non-good person may wield Butcher. It confers a +4 enhancement bonus to attack and damage rolls, as well as a +4 luck bonus to AC and CMD. In addition, it acts as a permanent lesser globe of invulnerability for the wielder only. Finally, it is the key to escape from this level of the dungeon.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +4 longsword</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p></p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Rappan Athuk",
